<p class="page" id="a4887006">[Page 6]</p>
<p>Hun have just one more chance at me.</p>
<p>Charlie Waterhouse has been killed and one of the Searles has gone home to Sydney.  Both come from Auburn &amp; know you I think.</p>
<p>Well, I'll look forward to hearing from you shortly.  At present I'm under isolation, as some mug in the hut has mumps, so I am filling in the time reading again Homer's Odyssey and the Iliads, which are the best sleep producers, barring howitzer shells, I know of.</p>
<p>Your old Pal<br/>Arthur</p>
